Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"There are so many\Npeople on this big old Earth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"And it's a miracle\Nthat I've met you here"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"The place we're born,\Nthe language we speak"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"The color of our eyes"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"My style, my dreams, my personality"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}On the evening of the 7th
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}a truck and bus collided\Nin Kiyu Haragi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Naoki Horikawa,\Na freshman at a local high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}was involved in the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}and passed away\Nin a nearby hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The police have not ruled\Nout the possibility of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}They said it might be suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Of course it's suicide.\NHe was in pretty bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}So what are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know if I've got time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Time? Time for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- No...\N- You've got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Actually...\N- What? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"Game over"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sorry, Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You just kept saying you were sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Um... Horikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You can call me Anna. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Well... What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's a really exciting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm surprised\Nyou've got a talent like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm surprised\Nyou've got a talent like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Talent?\NIt's really nothing that special...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You just got caught here, but\Nyou can hide in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}As you play the game, you can\Nchoose the wrong route, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Do you have to start over from\Nwhere you made the mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You don't need to\Nstart over, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's a special program
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}that activates if you don't give up\Neven when things get really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A special program?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah. You ran into this\Nroom and couldn't go on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Even if you make this choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's made so that if don't\Ngive up, you can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's like... the strength\Nto open the door you closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And face the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The strength to face the danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah. Actually there's similar\Nprograms besides this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's a slightly\Ndifferent program...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's a secret item inside this desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What happened to your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm fine. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sorry to keep you out here so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The game was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Thanks for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I was happy when you talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Since you just moved here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}there's probably a lot\Nyou don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I want to do some maintenance,\Nso go home without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Talent, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I have to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You don't look like you're doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}An escape game? What, did you make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"Blue Green Ghost"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}My mom's gonna worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're such a mama's boy, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}That's why Takuro bullies you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}That's not it.\NI've got good reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oh, Takuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Okay, let's do some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}More drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Wait, does it really\Nhave to be here, Takuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This place is you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We can leave them here and\Nnobody will find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I spread a rumor that\Nthere were ghosts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Right, Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The Jailhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We're best buddies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm counting on you, best bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Come on, hurry.\NThe sun's going to set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah. Takeshi, you push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah. Takeshi, you push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Shut up!\N- Takeshi's scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}He doesn't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Stop talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This place is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This is my territory, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't\Nthink anybody lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Forget the excuses.\NJust tell me what you're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Have you ever heard of holometabolism?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's when an insect transforms\Nvia a cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Don't you think it's a\Nstrange, wonderful mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A caterpillar turns into a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And I'm going to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And just a while ago,\NI caught a bombardier beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}When a bombardier beetle is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}they emit a noxious\Nspray out of their butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Can you believe that?\NIsn't it wonderfully mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And the way the bombardier beetle\Nstarts to panic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}and resist when you catch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's so cute! So cute! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Listen.\NI'm not asking about the bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm not interested in human\Nbiology at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}nor in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shut up-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Your faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm going to go finish\Nsomething. You guys wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Don't let anybody in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The door... that sound...\Nthis is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You guys are all crazy, coming\Ninto a creepy place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"Reject. Answer"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"No signal"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What? No signal? Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm sure it's Takuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Takeshi!\N- Oh no! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What's wrong? Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why won't it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There was something I wanted to check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}More importantly, what\Nhappened? Takeshi was acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Something weird, a guy\Nwe've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But... I think I've seen\Nhim before, somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You've seen him? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna, let's get out of\Nhere! I've got a bad feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But Shun, the front door won't open,\Nand all the windows are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We should get everybody back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro! Takuro! Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I can't take anymore! No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What is this place? Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The door... the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Okay,\Nlet's stash the stuff down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Not you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Well, it is creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'd never come here if I didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}So like, I know it's creepy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What, exactly, is creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you trying to say is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}That's hilarious. I haven't\Ntalked about ghosts in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Come on, don't be\Nstupid. Let's finish this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm going down, you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.71,0:24:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's something\Nhere! It was looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.48,0:24:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.31,0:25:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There may be someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.37,0:25:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Forgot it! Let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.84,0:25:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's not do this, Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.66,0:26:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Don't scare me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.03,0:26:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.99,0:26:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's something here! I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.76,0:26:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro's always like this.\NIt was the same with Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.69,0:26:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.50,0:26:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}If you say another\Nword, Takuro will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.12,0:26:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi, there's no point in staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.39,0:26:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.59,0:27:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This building's kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.61,0:27:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.12,0:27:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.19,0:27:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.78,0:27:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Our parents are going to start to freak out
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.62,0:27:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}when we don't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.38,0:27:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And then they'll find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.64,0:27:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'll stay here until that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.85,0:27:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm not doing that. I want to\Nget out of here as fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.25,0:27:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You can do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.58,0:27:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Alright.\NAnyway, we're heading outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}When we get out,\Nwe'll call your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.91,0:27:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}so stay here until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.35,0:28:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi? May I borrow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.97,0:28:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.87,0:28:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.07,0:28:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Bye. Wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.73,0:29:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.02,0:29:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.83,0:29:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.46,0:29:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Well...\N- Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.66,0:29:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Did anything strange happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.26,0:29:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The front door just\Nwouldn't open all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.58,0:29:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.12,0:29:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's one shivering in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.39,0:29:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Where's Takuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:30:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know. I lost him midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.55,0:30:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro might know something, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.61,0:30:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Where do you suppose he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.31,0:30:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I can't take anymore... I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.05,0:30:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why do I have to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Freaking Takuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.31,0:30:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hello? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The Jailhouse! The Jailhouse!\NBehind the abandoned school!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.07,0:30:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.17,0:31:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What's wrong? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.77,0:31:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro, let's get out of\Nhere! There's a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.60,0:31:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.94,0:31:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.10,0:31:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.20,0:31:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi! Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.40,0:31:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi! What's wrong? Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.68,0:32:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.11,0:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know who did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.58,0:32:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}but we need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.18,0:32:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey, where's the key to the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.30,0:32:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro's got it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.88,0:32:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika, where is Takuro right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.60,0:32:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We got separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.84,0:32:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.88,0:32:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.80,0:32:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi's been brutally\Nkilled, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.64,0:32:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you trying to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.64,0:32:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What is Takuro doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.56,0:32:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.17,0:32:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.77,0:32:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.67,0:32:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What did Takeshi mean when\Nhe mentioned Naoki back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.30,0:33:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You said if he said anymore,\NTakuro would kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.60,0:33:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.60,0:33:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What is Takuro doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.36,0:33:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know!\NIt's got nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.65,0:33:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Tell me why Naoki died?\N- I said I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.63,0:33:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.69,0:33:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun, we need to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.86,0:33:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun? Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.65,0:33:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.12,0:33:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun, we need to hurry and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.72,0:33:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.38,0:33:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Do you remember this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.72,0:33:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.05,0:33:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's the exact same as the game I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.68,0:34:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.92,0:34:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika, you were\Nwatching up there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.35,0:34:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Listen, Takuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.78,0:34:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi... He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.24,0:34:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}He was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.64,0:34:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's a monster here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We need to hurry or we'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.95,0:34:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.70,0:34:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You've been using too many\Ndrugs, haven't you Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.74,0:34:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sure, sure. Just keep\Nwatch. I'll be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.24,0:35:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'll give you plenty of attention later,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.51,0:35:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}so just wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.63,0:35:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No, Takuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.86,0:35:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I can't hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.49,0:35:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.30,0:35:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.29,0:35:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.96,0:35:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.49,0:35:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Bye, Takuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.92,0:35:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Huh? You're not going to finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.25,0:36:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.45,0:36:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna, would you pull a book off\Nthe bookshelf
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.08,0:36:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}at the same time I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.78,0:36:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This book.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.36,0:36:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.61,0:36:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.41,0:36:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.35,0:36:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A key?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.56,0:36:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.95,0:36:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's the same as the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.44,0:36:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.62,0:36:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey, Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.38,0:36:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.52,0:36:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.24,0:37:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.04,0:37:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.80,0:38:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.88,0:39:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.18,0:39:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.78,0:39:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika! Mika! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.04,0:39:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika! Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.68,0:39:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.71,0:40:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.12,0:41:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Next is the piano room.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.49,0:41:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:41:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.76,0:41:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.61,0:41:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.44,0:42:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}That's not Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.65,0:42:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna... Shun... save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.35,0:42:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.39,0:42:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun...\NMika would never call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.94,0:42:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Please. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.82,0:42:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}She wouldn't call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.08,0:42:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.68,0:42:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.08,0:42:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun! Shun! Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.80,0:42:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun! Shun! Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.34,0:42:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun! Shun! Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.67,0:42:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.13,0:42:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Save me, Shun. I'm Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.27,0:42:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.87,0:43:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The Ao Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.87,0:43:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.73,0:43:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.19,0:43:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's a handkerchief inside\Nhere. You put the liquid soap on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.22,0:44:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.52,0:44:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.61,0:44:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.22,0:45:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.64,0:45:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun, where do we go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.21,0:45:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The piano room. Wipe the keys\Nwith this and you'll see a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.30,0:45:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You can use it to open the safe\Nin the next room
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.10,0:45:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}to get a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.04,0:45:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Roll back the carpet in the storeroom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.28,0:45:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}and you'll see a secret staircase...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.26,0:45:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}How did you know\Nit wasn't Mika back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.33,0:46:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.44,0:46:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You look like Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.43,0:46:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Did anybody ever tell\Nyou about my little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.23,0:46:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Naoki Horikawa,\Nwho died six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.82,0:46:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}He's two years younger than me,\Nand we went to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.03,0:46:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Since we were so close in\Nage, we fought all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.96,0:46:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.32,0:46:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}He was being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.05,0:46:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I could tell it, somehow, so I\Nasked Naoki a bunch of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.96,0:47:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You can tell your big\Nsister anything, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.12,0:47:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But he always said he was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.99,0:47:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And he'd smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.05,0:47:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Whenever he smiled and\Nsaid he was okay, it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.28,0:47:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're a lot like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.14,0:47:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Naoki is telling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.48,0:47:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Naoki is telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.58,0:47:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Is that how you knew about the Ao Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.75,0:47:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.28,0:48:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! I'm so glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.24,0:48:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.57,0:48:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.24,0:48:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hiroshi,\Nwe may be able to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.53,0:48:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Alright. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.75,0:49:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No, Takuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.43,0:49:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I can't hold back anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.21,0:49:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hey... it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.02,0:49:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.45,0:49:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I can't hold back anymore either!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.45,0:50:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.08,0:50:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}This is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.21,0:50:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- A game?\N- It's a game world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.41,0:50:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A game world? How unrealistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.62,0:50:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Next we go to the storeroom\Nand roll back the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.58,0:50:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}And then we'll see the\Nentrance to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.85,0:50:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.85,0:50:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's end this game. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.91,0:50:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.31,0:50:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.43,0:51:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.09,0:51:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Not that it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.29,0:51:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why? Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.53,0:51:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}If you don't leave with us, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.80,0:51:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Die? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.49,0:51:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.49,0:51:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.96,0:51:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't have the slightest\Nclue who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.02,0:51:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.23,0:52:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Your brother died on his own, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.29,0:52:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I was just a little mean to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.56,0:52:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}We're going to end this. Right, Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.12,0:52:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.58,0:52:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yes. This is a game Shun made.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.22,0:52:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.05,0:52:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oh, do you like this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.39,0:52:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.09,0:52:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You took Shun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.95,0:52:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.11,0:52:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Stop talking about Shun all the darn time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.37,0:52:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Out with it.\NWhat do you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.15,0:52:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.45,0:52:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Are you talking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.74,0:53:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.61,0:53:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're getting creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.95,0:53:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna Horikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.96,0:54:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.86,0:54:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.99,0:54:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.79,0:54:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.53,0:54:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.60,0:54:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun, Mika wouldn't call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.87,0:54:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}She wouldn't call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.57,0:54:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}How did you know it wasn't Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.87,0:55:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.70,0:55:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.70,0:55:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Do you believe what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.63,0:55:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.19,0:55:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You know all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.72,0:56:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You can't leave alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.24,0:56:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun... you may not be able to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.32,0:56:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But Takuro killed my\Nbrother Naoki, and you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.19,0:56:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun was using my name in a game he made!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.91,0:56:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It really made me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.69,0:56:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.35,0:56:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oh? And?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.17,0:56:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.68,0:56:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No way. I'm done talking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.41,0:56:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}He's been with me this\Nwhole time, helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.68,0:56:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I thought he was alive like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.24,0:56:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Right, Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.11,0:57:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}But I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.50,0:57:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I knew the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.38,0:57:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}When I came here, you were already...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.74,0:57:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}When I came here, you were already...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.80,0:57:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.94,0:57:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.93,0:57:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I wanted to take care of that\Nand go home with everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.60,0:57:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The only thing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.26,0:57:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}is give you a peaceful death.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.86,0:57:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It would be better if you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.72,0:57:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}It would be better if you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.60,0:58:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}You're the ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.86,0:58:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}who are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.59,0:58:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No, you're the one who's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.59,0:58:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.19,0:58:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hiroshi! Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.36,0:58:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.06,0:58:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Hiroshi!\N- Let's go! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.52,0:59:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.14,0:59:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna... leave me and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.32,0:59:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No! Hiroshi, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.18,0:59:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.40,0:59:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.60,0:59:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.68,0:59:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.26,1:00:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.90,1:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.56,1:01:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.40,1:01:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I can't remember what to do!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.63,1:01:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.19,1:01:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.29,1:01:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.69,1:01:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.13,1:01:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.59,1:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.22,1:01:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}There's a special program
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.32,1:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}that activates if you don't give up\Neven when things get really bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.62,1:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Naoki would always\Nsay it's okay, and smile...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.62,1:01:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Whenever he smiled and\Nsaid he was okay, it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.71,1:01:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Anna! Anna! Anna!\N- It hurt...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.65,1:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.98,1:02:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna! Anna! Anna!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.89,1:02:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.41,1:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Why? Why do you say you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.67,1:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.04,1:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.53,1:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.33,1:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anna? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.40,1:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.83,1:03:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.06,1:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I'm sorry. Was it that scary?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.97,1:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.80,1:03:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I just remembered a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.29,1:03:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}The strength to face the danger, was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.56,1:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- Huh?\N- That special program you made.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.60,1:03:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.83,1:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Shun...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.65,1:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}I couldn't save my\Nlittle brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.32,1:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}{\be30}Tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.12,1:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.35,1:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.89,1:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.51,1:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"Clear"
